---
title: Turkish-Spiced Lamb with Pickled Cabbage and Garlic Toum Sauce
description: In this tasty Turkish-style salad, juicy seared lamb gets tossed in spices and rested atop fresh peas with crunchy pickled red cabbage. Enjoy with a classic creamy garlic toum sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkish-spiced-lamb-871a982c.jpg
